    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl03_LabelType\">You carry a non-masterwork simple or martial weapon that has been passed down from generation to generation in your family (pay the standard gp cost for the weapon).</span></p></em>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl03_LabelType\">When you select this trait, choose one of the following benefits: proficiency with that specific weapon, a +1 trait bonus on attacks of opportunity with that specific weapon, or a +2 trait bonus on one kind of combat maneuver when using that specific weapon.</span><br /></span></p>",
